reviewText: I am so glad I found this DVD.  I enjoy his singing and its nice to see him in concert.  Thanks.
I can't believe more people didn't see this special. SO amazing. He will go far!

Nathan Pcheco has a beautiful voice but more than that he gives off happy vibes as if he enjoys life to the fullest and he sends this message to you.  So yes this get 5 stars and would get 10 if offered.
